<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "profile.jpg", width: 300, alt: "profile image", class: 'profile-jpg', class: 'profile-img' %>
        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div 
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                ></div>
              </div>
            </div>
           
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>Thanks for visiting me at my website. Every time I work I have a great passion to do it. My years of experience are. 1. Video editor for 5 years with Adobe Premire. 2. Worked at a Bakery for a summer. 3. TKD for 4 years. 4. Did a summer camp on coding and still learning more now.5. Have been doing lawns for 5 years also. The thing I want to do when I get older is be a director and writer. </p>
      </div>
      
      <p>
        <button
          class="btn btn-primary"
          type="button"
          data-toggle="collapse"
          data-target="#jobHistory"
          aria-expanded="false"
          aria-controller="jobHistory"
        >
          Job History
        </button>
        
        <button
          class="btn btn-primary"
          type="button"
          data-toggle="collapse"
          data-target="#education"
          aria-expanded="false"
          aria-controller="education"
        >
          Education
        </button>
      </p>
      
      <p>
        <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
          <div class="card card-block">
            Jobsssss
          </div>
          <div class="card card-block">
            Lawn mowing
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="collapse" id="education">
          <div class="card card-block">
            School 1
          </div>
          <div class="card card-block">
            School 2
          </div>
        </div>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>